reviewText: Honestly this season sucks, its barely holding my interests. Its completely random at this point.
Its a little like Girls Bravo only yuri. It is the 2nd season of Maria Holic but should be named Kanako Holic Alive instead.
The series is great! Hillarious! The only thing that sucked was there was no commentary. But again, this is a good addition to my yuri collection. And a nice twist to a coming of age comedy
The item arrived and works I am satisfied
